---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout pageKey="consent-policy.html">

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white py-24">

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">

<div class="uppercase tracking-widest text-sm text-indigo-300 mb-4">
CONSENT & DATA RIGHTS
</div>

<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
Consent Policy
</h1>

<p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
How Solar AI Advisor collects, records, manages and respects your consent.
</p>

<p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-6">
Last Updated: June 2026
</p>

</div>

</section>

<section class="py-20">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

<div class="space-y-8">

<!-- SECTION 1 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
1. Purpose Of This Policy
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
This Consent Policy explains how Solar AI Advisor obtains, manages, stores and uses consent when processing personal information and providing services through the platform.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
This policy should be read together with our Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 2 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
2. Consent Principles
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Solar AI Advisor seeks consent that is:
</p>

<ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-slate-600">

<li>• Free and voluntary</li>

<li>• Specific and informed</li>

<li>• Clear and unambiguous</li>

<li>• Limited to legitimate purposes</li>

<li>• Withdrawable at any time</li>

</ul>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 3 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
3. Consent For Solar Assessments
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
By submitting your electricity bill information, property details, location data or other assessment inputs, you consent to Solar AI Advisor processing that information to generate solar recommendations and estimates.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
This may include AI-powered calculations, financial projections, suitability scoring and report generation.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 4 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
4. Consent For AI Analysis
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Users acknowledge that Solar AI Advisor may use automated systems, algorithms and artificial intelligence technologies to analyze submitted information.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
By using the platform, users consent to such automated processing for the purpose of generating recommendations and insights.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 5 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
5. Consent For Document Uploads
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
When uploading electricity bills, quotations, photographs or related documents, users consent to Solar AI Advisor reviewing, storing and processing those materials for service delivery purposes.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Uploaded documents may be used for analysis, verification, quote reviews, installer matching and customer support activities.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 6 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
6. Consent For Installer Matching
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Where users request installer assistance, site surveys, quotations or project support, users consent to Solar AI Advisor sharing relevant information with selected installation partners.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Information shared will be limited to what is reasonably necessary for the requested service.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 7 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
7. Consent For Communications
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
By providing contact information, users consent to receiving communications related to their solar enquiry, assessment, installer matching request, quote review or project support request.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Communications may occur through:
</p>

<ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-slate-600">

<li>• Phone calls</li>

<li>• SMS messages</li>

<li>• WhatsApp messages</li>

<li>• Email communications</li>

<li>• In-app notifications</li>

</ul>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 8 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
8. Consent For Site Surveys
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Where a user requests a physical site survey, technical assessment or installer visit, Solar AI Advisor may share relevant contact and property information with a selected installation partner.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Users consent to such information sharing solely for arranging and conducting the requested service.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 9 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
9. Consent For Quote Reviews
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Users may voluntarily upload solar quotations, proposals and related documents for independent review.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
By submitting such documents, users consent to Solar AI Advisor analyzing those materials and generating informational observations, recommendations and insights.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 10 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
10. Withdrawal Of Consent
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Upon withdrawal of consent, Solar AI Advisor immediately ceases processing and sharing of personal data associated with the user. Account access is disabled and records are scheduled for secure deletion within a reasonable operational period, typically within 24 hours, unless retention is required by applicable law.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Withdrawal of consent may limit our ability to provide certain services, assessments, installer matching functions or support activities.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Withdrawal will not affect processing already completed before the withdrawal request was received.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 11 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
11. Consent Records
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Solar AI Advisor may maintain records demonstrating when and how consent was obtained.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
These records may include timestamps, consent acknowledgements, form submissions and related audit information.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 12 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
12. Digital Personal Data Protection Act (DPDP Act)
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Solar AI Advisor seeks to process personal information in accordance with applicable Indian privacy laws, including the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023, where applicable.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Users may exercise rights available under applicable law, including requesting information regarding personal data processing and seeking correction or deletion where legally permissible.
</p>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 13 -->

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-sm">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
13. Changes To This Policy
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
Solar AI Advisor may revise this Consent Policy from time to time to reflect legal, operational or technological changes.
</p>

<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
Updated versions will be published on this page together with the revised effective date.
</p>

</div>

<!-- CONTACT -->

<div class="bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-200 rounded-3xl p-8">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
Questions About Consent?
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
For consent requests, withdrawal requests, privacy enquiries or compliance questions, please contact:
</p>

<div class="mt-6">

<p class="font-semibold">
Solar AI Advisor
</p>

<p class="mt-2">
support@solaraiadvisor.in
</p>

<p class="mt-2">
www.solaraiadvisor.in
</p>

</div>

</div>

<!-- LEGAL NOTICE -->

<div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-3xl p-8">

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-800 mb-4">
Important Notice
</h2>

<p class="text-amber-900 leading-relaxed">
Consent provided through Solar AI Advisor is voluntary and may be withdrawn at any time. However, certain services may not be available if required consent is withdrawn.
</p>

<p class="text-amber-900 leading-relaxed mt-4">
By using the platform, users acknowledge that they have read, understood and agreed to this Consent Policy together with the Privacy Policy and Terms of Service.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<!-- CTA -->

<section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-24 text-center">

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
Ready To Explore Solar?
</h2>

<p class="text-slate-300 text-lg mb-8">
Get your personalized solar assessment in under a minute.
</p>

<a href="index.html"
class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold">
Calculate My Solar Savings
</a>

</div>

</section>

</BaseLayout>
